    "faq": {
      "heading": "Quick answers",
      "items": [
        {
          "q": "What is an AI agent?",
          "a": "Software that does a job, not just answers. It acts across your tools, within rules you set."
        },
        {
          "q": "How fast is it live?",
          "a": "Most agents launch in under 30 days. Complex setups take 6–8 weeks."
        },
        {
          "q": "What do you need from us?",
          "a": "Nothing technical. Just a few hours from whoever knows the process best."
        },
        {
          "q": "What if it makes a mistake?",
          "a": "Anything ambiguous or sensitive goes to a human, full conversation attached."
        },
        {
          "q": "GDPR and data security?",
          "a": "Everything stays in the EU, encrypted. We sign a DPA with every client."
        },
        {
          "q": "Does it work with my tools?",
          "a": "Anything with an API — that's almost everything. No API? We bridge it."
        },
        {
          "q": "What happens after launch?",
          "a": "Monitoring, tuning and a monthly report with hard numbers. Launch is the start."
        }
      ]
    },
